    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/46ea506e47eef9a026ee7cf33fcc26d2.poster.avif?t=1732938331\" width=684 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/46ea506e47eef9a026ee7cf33fcc26d2.webm?t=1732938331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/46ea506e47eef9a026ee7cf33fcc26d2.mp4?t=1732938331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A classic platformer</strong><br>Embark on a magical journey as Squirrel Knight on his quest to save the forest. Squirrel Knight is an action-platformer game with upgradable abilities, time trials  and challenging bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/17d5f2ae1ff85dbce50cc1507c238c07.poster.avif?t=1732938331\" width=684 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/17d5f2ae1ff85dbce50cc1507c238c07.webm?t=1732938331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/17d5f2ae1ff85dbce50cc1507c238c07.mp4?t=1732938331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Battle powerful bosses</strong><br>Fight in Boss Rush mode and overcome powered up foes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/178f74a395ebdf06f27a443a6adc55c4.poster.avif?t=1732938331\" width=684 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1828450/extras/178f74a395ebdf06f27a443a6adc55c4